   CONVERSION INDUSTRIES Inc. (Pasadena, Calif.) -- William
M. Hitchcock and D. Grant Macdonald were named to the board
of this independent power-production company, expanding the
size of the board to seven members. Conversion said Mr.
Hitchcock is managing partner of Bedford Street Group, a
Santa Monica, Calif., investment-management company and Mr.
Macdonald is a director of Yorkton Continental Securities
Inc., a Toronto-based securities brokerage firm.
